# Summary
This documentation page explains Amplitude's "Releases" feature, which tracks product changes as markers on time-series charts, detailing how automated releases work for Growth/Enterprise plans using semantic versioning, manual release creation for Plus plans, and the Release Timeline/Report functionality for analyzing user response to product changes.

